title: Trump Shows Support for McCarthy as Speaker, but McConnell Would Be Out
description: The former president said that, if he runs for president and wins in 2024, Senator Mitch McConnell will “be out in two minutes.”
dc:creator: Annie Karni
media:credit: Maddie McGarvey for The New York Times
media:description: Former President Donald J. Trump speaks in Dayton, Ohio, on Monday.
